This product includes software developed by:
- The World Bank Group (https://www.worldbank.org/)
- Contributors to the JurisAI project

This software uses the following open source packages:
- OpenAI GPT models for legal analysis
- Google Cloud Translation API for language translation
- Pinecone for vector similarity search
- FastAPI for backend services
- Streamlit for frontend interface
- LangChain for AI orchestration

Legal Resources provided by:
- Ghana Legal Information Institute (GhaLII)
- Sierra Leone Legal Information Institute (SierraLII)

The views expressed in this software do not necessarily represent those of the World Bank Group, 
its Board of Executive Directors, or the governments they represent. 